WEBVTT

00:00:00.320 --> 00:00:02.590
Good morning, family. I know you're

00:00:02.600 --> 00:00:05.470
used to seeing my husband, but today it's

00:00:05.480 --> 00:00:08.350
just me. I have some things that

00:00:08.360 --> 00:00:09.950
I feel the Lord wants me to share

00:00:09.960 --> 00:00:12.230
with you, so we're just going to get

00:00:12.240 --> 00:00:17.670
right into it. Last night, I had a

00:00:17.680 --> 00:00:20.790
dream.

00:00:20.800 --> 00:00:22.509
Before I get to the dream, I've been

00:00:22.519 --> 00:00:25.750
reading this book, 'Killing Kryptonite.'It's by John Bevere and it's called 'Killing

00:00:25.760 --> 00:00:28.509
Kryptonite:

00:00:28.519 --> 00:00:31.150
Destroy What Steals

00:00:31.160 --> 00:00:34.389
Your

00:00:34.389 --> 00:00:34.399
Strength.'The

00:00:34.399 --> 00:00:37.270
Lord has been talking to me

00:00:37.270 --> 00:00:37.280
because

00:00:37.280 --> 00:00:41.310
I call

00:00:41.320 --> 00:00:45.630
myself a 'book snob.'I really know

00:00:45.630 --> 00:00:45.640
which

00:00:45.640 --> 00:00:47.910
books feed

00:00:47.920 --> 00:00:50.910
my spirit. If

00:00:50.920 --> 00:00:53.229
the books I've suggested have

00:00:53.239 --> 00:00:55.549
been a help to you, the Lord has been

00:00:55.559 --> 00:00:57.270
telling me to create a

00:00:57.270 --> 00:00:57.280
Goodreads

00:00:57.280 --> 00:00:59.709
account so people who want to

00:00:59.719 --> 00:01:01.270
know what

00:01:01.270 --> 00:01:01.280
I'm

00:01:01.280 --> 00:01:03.709
reading can find them. I'm

00:01:03.709 --> 00:01:03.719
always reading, so I'll

00:01:03.719 --> 00:01:05.830
be putting those on my

00:01:05.840 --> 00:01:07.789
Goodreads account bookshelves

00:01:07.799 --> 00:01:09.350
so you can see what I'm reading,

00:01:09.360 --> 00:01:11.190
what I've read, and the stars

00:01:11.200 --> 00:01:13.429
I've given. I will put that link

00:01:13.439 --> 00:01:16.230
in the description if you want to

00:01:16.240 --> 00:01:19.710
see about that. Anyway,

00:01:19.710 --> 00:01:19.720
regarding

00:01:19.720 --> 00:01:21.830
this book: when we've said

00:01:21.840 --> 00:01:23.870
there will be a revival in these

00:01:23.880 --> 00:01:26.630
last days, we have gotten emails and

00:01:26.640 --> 00:01:29.030
comments challenging that, asking where that

00:01:29.030 --> 00:01:29.040
is

00:01:29.040 --> 00:01:30.630
in the Bible.

00:01:30.640 --> 00:01:33.190
It's

00:01:33.200 --> 00:01:34.590
interesting because the Lord led me to

00:01:34.600 --> 00:01:36.310
this book, and

00:01:36.320 --> 00:01:39.510
it has several scriptures

00:01:39.520 --> 00:01:42.270
backing that there will be a revival

00:01:42.280 --> 00:01:43.590
in the last days. I'm going to

00:01:43.600 --> 00:01:46.870
read this part from page 68 for

00:01:46.870 --> 00:01:46.880
anyone

00:01:46.880 --> 00:01:49.709
who wants to get the book. It

00:01:49.719 --> 00:01:52.389
says, 'Let me start by sharing an

00:01:52.399 --> 00:01:54.950
experience in prayer I'll never forget. I

00:01:54.960 --> 00:01:57.749
heard so clearly: Son, the book of Acts

00:01:57.759 --> 00:01:59.350
will seem like child's play in

00:01:59.360 --> 00:02:01.310
comparison to what I'm about to do in and

00:02:01.320 --> 00:02:03.270
through the church prior to my Son's

00:02:03.280 --> 00:02:07.149
return. I was in shock. In fact, I didn't

00:02:07.159 --> 00:02:09.550
believe what I had heard. I countered by

00:02:09.560 --> 00:02:11.830
saying: Father, I need three different

00:02:11.840 --> 00:02:13.869
references from the Bible to believe

00:02:13.879 --> 00:02:16.710
this. Interestingly, I sensed no

00:02:16.720 --> 00:02:19.470
displeasure in asking for this. We are to

00:02:19.480 --> 00:02:23.030
test all things (1 Thessalonians) and

00:02:23.040 --> 00:02:25.270
are told: by the mouth of two or three

00:02:25.280 --> 00:02:27.990
witnesses let every word be established

00:02:28.000 --> 00:02:31.070
(2 Corinthians 13:1).'One of the references

00:02:31.080 --> 00:02:33.030
He directed me to is the

00:02:33.040 --> 00:02:35.509
scripture: 'For thus says the Lord of

00:02:35.519 --> 00:02:38.790
hosts: Once more (it is a little while) I

00:02:38.800 --> 00:02:41.390
will shake heaven and earth, the sea and

00:02:41.400 --> 00:02:44.350
dry land; and I will shake all nations,

00:02:44.360 --> 00:02:46.589
and they shall come to the Desire of All

00:02:46.599 --> 00:02:49.190
Nations, and I will fill this temple

00:02:49.200 --> 00:02:51.630
with glory, says the Lord of hosts. The

00:02:51.640 --> 00:02:54.070
glory of this latter temple shall be

00:02:54.080 --> 00:02:56.030
greater than the former, says the Lord of

00:02:56.030 --> 00:02:56.040
hosts.'That

00:02:56.040 --> 00:02:58.830
is

00:02:58.830 --> 00:02:58.840
Haggai

00:02:58.840 --> 00:03:01.430
2:6-7 and 9. So, what about the time

00:03:01.440 --> 00:03:03.110
period? Is Haggai discussing the church

00:03:03.120 --> 00:03:05.390
from beginning to end? In other words, is

00:03:05.400 --> 00:03:07.430
it from the time of Jesus'ascension to

00:03:07.440 --> 00:03:08.990
the time of His second coming? Look again

00:03:09.000 --> 00:03:11.430
at God's words as written

00:03:11.440 --> 00:03:14.110
down by Haggai: 'Once more (it is a little

00:03:14.120 --> 00:03:16.110
while) I will shake the heaven and the

00:03:16.120 --> 00:03:17.670
earth, the sea and the dry land; and I

00:03:17.680 --> 00:03:19.630
will shake all nations, and they shall

00:03:19.640 --> 00:03:21.509
come to the Desire of All Nations, and I

00:03:21.519 --> 00:03:23.470
will fill this temple with

00:03:23.470 --> 00:03:23.480
glory.'The

00:03:23.480 --> 00:03:25.830
glory he refers to occurs in this time

00:03:25.840 --> 00:03:28.589
period. The shaking occurs. He makes

00:03:28.599 --> 00:03:30.710
another promise: 'Once again I will shake

00:03:30.720 --> 00:03:33.030
not only the earth but the heavens

00:03:33.030 --> 00:03:33.040
also.'This

00:03:33.040 --> 00:03:34.789
means that all of creation will be

00:03:34.799 --> 00:03:37.070
shaken and removed so that only

00:03:37.080 --> 00:03:39.390
unshakable things will

00:03:39.400 --> 00:03:41.110
remain.

00:03:41.120 --> 00:03:44.190
A well-established pattern is seen

00:03:44.200 --> 00:03:46.470
throughout scripture: God always saves

00:03:46.480 --> 00:03:49.190
the best for last. We are told the end of

00:03:49.200 --> 00:03:50.869
a thing is better than its beginning

00:03:50.879 --> 00:03:53.550
(Ecclesiastes 7:8). Jesus displays this

00:03:53.560 --> 00:03:55.429
pattern by saving the best wine for

00:03:55.439 --> 00:03:57.509
last at the wedding of Cana. Later, He

00:03:57.519 --> 00:03:59.149
declares that anyone who believes in Me

00:03:59.159 --> 00:04:00.789
will do the same works I have done,

00:04:00.789 --> 00:04:00.799
and

00:04:00.799 --> 00:04:03.550
even greater works. Why

00:04:03.560 --> 00:04:05.309
would the greater come after Jesus has

00:04:05.319 --> 00:04:07.229
ascended? Because He always

00:04:07.239 --> 00:04:10.509
saves the best for last. The same is true

00:04:10.519 --> 00:04:12.190
for the church; its end will be better

00:04:12.200 --> 00:04:13.990
than its beginning. The book of Acts

00:04:14.000 --> 00:04:15.869
shows a remarkable beginning, so can you

00:04:15.879 --> 00:04:17.789
believe that the end of the

00:04:17.799 --> 00:04:19.509
church's time on Earth will be less

00:04:19.519 --> 00:04:22.230
glorious, powerful, and impactful

00:04:22.240 --> 00:04:24.469
than the beginning? Remember, Paul

00:04:24.479 --> 00:04:26.629
states your faith should

00:04:26.639 --> 00:04:28.710
not be in the wisdom of men but in the

00:04:28.720 --> 00:04:31.710
power of God, and again, that the kingdom

00:04:31.720 --> 00:04:34.390
of God is not in word but in power (1

00:04:34.400 --> 00:04:37.469
Corinthians 2:5). Power is a huge

00:04:37.479 --> 00:04:39.830
aspect of God's manifested kingdom on

00:04:39.840 --> 00:04:42.830
Earth. I thought that would

00:04:42.840 --> 00:04:45.670
help those of you who have asked.

00:04:45.680 --> 00:04:48.029
I'm excited and ready for it.

00:04:48.039 --> 00:04:49.510
There's going to be a great

00:04:49.520 --> 00:04:51.990
outpouring of miracles and

00:04:52.000 --> 00:04:54.790
healings;

00:04:54.800 --> 00:04:56.430
it's coming. Last

00:04:56.440 --> 00:04:58.870
night I had a dream, and in the dream, I

00:04:58.880 --> 00:05:02.189
saw what appeared to be a revival. I'm

00:05:02.199 --> 00:05:04.430
not going to name names,

00:05:04.440 --> 00:05:07.430
but

00:05:07.440 --> 00:05:10.230
there was a preacher up there

00:05:10.240 --> 00:05:12.590
and there were what appeared to be

00:05:12.590 --> 00:05:12.600
miracles—people

00:05:12.600 --> 00:05:15.230
being set free. It

00:05:15.240 --> 00:05:18.670
appeared that His glory was there;

00:05:18.680 --> 00:05:21.870
people were reacting as if it

00:05:21.880 --> 00:05:25.830
were, and there were signs of miracles

00:05:25.840 --> 00:05:29.390
being performed.

00:05:29.400 --> 00:05:33.309
It was on a massive scale.

00:05:37.039 --> 00:05:40.469
From the outside looking in,

00:05:40.479 --> 00:05:44.670
it appeared to be a mighty move of God,

00:05:44.680 --> 00:05:46.469
like an

00:05:46.469 --> 00:05:46.479
end-time

00:05:46.479 --> 00:05:50.670
revival. But as I was there, I

00:05:50.680 --> 00:05:52.629
sensed in my spirit that something

00:05:52.639 --> 00:05:55.270
wasn't right. This did not feel like the

00:05:55.280 --> 00:05:58.150
Lord. Then I heard the preacher

00:05:58.160 --> 00:06:00.070
saying, 'An even greater works will

00:06:00.080 --> 00:06:03.710
we do than what Jesus

00:06:03.710 --> 00:06:03.720
did.'But

00:06:03.720 --> 00:06:07.070
scripture says in Mark

00:06:07.070 --> 00:06:07.080
that

00:06:07.080 --> 00:06:09.270
false Christs and false prophets will

00:06:09.280 --> 00:06:11.469
arise and perform great signs and

00:06:11.479 --> 00:06:14.629
wonders so as to lead astray, if possible,

00:06:14.639 --> 00:06:18.150
even the elect. I felt in my spirit to

00:06:18.160 --> 00:06:20.909
warn you: do

00:06:20.919 --> 00:06:25.550
not be led astray by just miracles and

00:06:25.560 --> 00:06:29.270
performances, because they were

00:06:29.270 --> 00:06:29.280
twisting

00:06:29.280 --> 00:06:31.150
scripture. They weren't

00:06:31.160 --> 00:06:33.870
preaching the uncompromised Word of

00:06:33.880 --> 00:06:36.350
God.

00:06:37.800 --> 00:06:39.710
This

00:06:42.639 --> 00:06:45.550
is very serious.

00:06:45.560 --> 00:06:48.950
There will be people who

00:06:48.960 --> 00:06:52.309
profess they are of God,

00:06:52.309 --> 00:06:52.319
who

00:06:52.319 --> 00:06:54.029
are going to perform signs,

00:06:54.039 --> 00:06:56.029
wonders, healings,

00:06:56.029 --> 00:06:56.039
and

00:06:56.039 --> 00:06:57.990
manifestations of glory, but they're

00:06:58.000 --> 00:07:00.749
not going to be preaching that Jesus Christ

00:07:00.759 --> 00:07:02.830
is the same yesterday, today, and forever.

00:07:07.840 --> 00:07:09.670
They're going to

00:07:09.680 --> 00:07:11.790
twist it, saying there's more

00:07:11.800 --> 00:07:14.230
than one way to get to heaven, that you don't need just Jesus, or that you can serve other gods because God is universal. You're going to see them operate in giftings of the spirit, so to speak, but it is a demonic spirit trying to twist it. When you see people's eyes and ears open, it tries to sway people. They'll automatically think it has to be God, but the devil is a great deceiver. He is going to counterfeit it. That's what I heard in my spirit. The Lord said, 'Anything that I do, the devil tries to counterfeit.'He always wants to be greater than God. That was his whole agenda from the beginning; that was what caused his demise—trying to be equal with or better than Him, which we know is impossible, but he's still going to try. Just like it was with the children of Israel and Pharaoh's magicians. They were performing miracles too; they transformed their staffs into snakes. But even they had to eventually recognize the higher power and say Moses'God is God. They had to recognize the higher power even while trying to do their witchcraft to fool the people. The devil has power, but we have the Greater One. Diana had that dream, and the Lord told me to warn you that he's going to try to deceive the multitudes. You're going to have to be on guard, being filled with and controlled by the Holy Spirit in these last days so he is not able to snare you just because you see somebody get healed. I warned you about celebrities who get born again and say, 'We're on fire for Jesus,'then all of a sudden start preaching that there's

00:07:14.240 --> 00:07:16.070
more than one way to

00:07:16.070 --> 00:07:16.080
get to

00:07:16.080 --> 00:07:18.110
Jesus,

00:07:20.520 --> 00:07:22.390
or

00:09:59.760 --> 00:10:01.710
start

00:10:01.720 --> 00:10:05.430
talking about compromise and

00:10:05.440 --> 00:10:07.430
how you can live a compromising

00:10:07.430 --> 00:10:07.440
lifestyle—just

00:10:07.440 --> 00:10:10.350
so you can

00:10:10.350 --> 00:10:10.360
wallow

00:10:10.360 --> 00:10:13.550
in filth and not change,

00:10:13.560 --> 00:10:16.069
basically.

00:10:18.240 --> 00:10:19.590
It was just a bunch of

00:10:19.600 --> 00:10:24.069
sugar-coated poop.

00:10:29.560 --> 00:10:32.069
This is a time like never before for the

00:10:32.079 --> 00:10:33.990
body of Christ to have their discernment

00:10:34.000 --> 00:10:37.949
up.

00:10:37.959 --> 00:10:39.870
Be on guard. It's not time to let down

00:10:39.880 --> 00:10:42.710
and just go, 'Oh, the revival's

00:10:42.710 --> 00:10:42.720
here!'You've

00:10:42.720 --> 00:10:44.750
got to be on guard even in

00:10:44.760 --> 00:10:45.829
the midst of that. Scrutinize what

00:10:45.829 --> 00:10:45.839
they're

00:10:45.839 --> 00:10:47.990
preaching to

00:10:47.990 --> 00:10:48.000
make

00:10:48.000 --> 00:10:49.829
sure

00:10:49.829 --> 00:10:49.839
it's

00:10:49.839 --> 00:10:52.310
not a false gospel.

00:10:52.310 --> 00:10:52.320
I

00:10:52.320 --> 00:10:54.190
had that heavy on my spirit today

00:10:54.200 --> 00:10:56.269
after I woke up.

00:10:59.920 --> 00:11:02.310
It's important to tell

00:11:02.320 --> 00:11:04.310
the body of Christ

00:11:04.320 --> 00:11:06.310
because a lot of you are going

00:11:06.320 --> 00:11:08.750
to fall prey to it. We're so

00:11:08.760 --> 00:11:10.750
hungry and desperate for miracles;

00:11:10.760 --> 00:11:13.430
people are easily wooed by the

00:11:13.440 --> 00:11:16.949
supernatural,

00:11:16.959 --> 00:11:20.389
whether dark or light.

00:11:20.399 --> 00:11:22.310
That's why witchcraft is exploding

00:11:22.320 --> 00:11:23.550
in the United States; people are

00:11:27.480 --> 00:11:30.310
hungry for change. If they're not

00:11:30.320 --> 00:11:33.509
seeing it in the church,

00:11:37.120 --> 00:11:38.990
they're going to find something

00:11:42.680 --> 00:11:44.710
authentic elsewhere

00:11:44.710 --> 00:11:44.720
and get

00:11:44.720 --> 00:11:46.389
a hold of

00:11:46.399 --> 00:11:49.550
a rattlesnake. I

00:11:49.550 --> 00:11:49.560
don't

00:11:49.560 --> 00:11:51.670
think people

00:11:51.680 --> 00:11:54.910
realize

00:12:13.079 --> 00:12:16.269
how closely he's going

00:12:16.279 --> 00:12:18.870
to try to imitate it. That's the part

00:12:18.880 --> 00:12:21.710
that alarmed me in the dream.

00:12:25.800 --> 00:12:28.269
It looked identical from the

00:12:28.279 --> 00:12:29.949
outside.

00:12:29.959 --> 00:12:32.189
The only

00:12:32.199 --> 00:12:35.150
reason I knew was in my spirit; my

00:12:35.160 --> 00:12:38.110
spirit felt

00:12:38.110 --> 00:12:38.120
dirty.

00:12:38.120 --> 00:12:40.670
God

00:12:40.670 --> 00:12:40.680
is clean

00:12:40.680 --> 00:12:43.910
and

00:12:43.910 --> 00:12:43.920
holy.

00:12:43.920 --> 00:12:47.150
It

00:12:47.160 --> 00:12:49.870
was disturbing how closely he

00:12:49.880 --> 00:12:54.829
mimicked it

00:13:04.430 --> 00:13:04.440
to

00:13:14.670 --> 00:13:14.680
a

00:13:22.040 --> 00:13:24.189
tee.

00:13:35.279 --> 00:13:39.269
It

00:13:39.279 --> 00:13:41.189
raised the hairs on

00:13:41.189 --> 00:13:41.199
my

00:13:41.199 --> 00:13:43.509
skin;

00:13:43.519 --> 00:13:45.189
I had chills in a

00:13:45.199 --> 00:13:48.710
bad way, and I wanted to get out of

00:13:48.720 --> 00:13:51.350
there.

00:13:57.959 --> 00:14:00.030
It's coming like a freight

00:14:00.040 --> 00:14:03.470
train.

00:14:03.480 --> 00:14:05.509
Look at that scripture:

00:14:05.519 --> 00:14:09.550
'even the

00:14:09.550 --> 00:14:09.560
elect.'Even

00:14:09.560 --> 00:14:12.230
the Christians

00:14:12.240 --> 00:14:14.550
who should know better

00:14:14.560 --> 00:14:18.230
will be deceived. That

00:14:18.240 --> 00:14:19.990
means they're going

00:14:20.000 --> 00:14:22.710
to be good at what they do.

00:14:22.720 --> 00:14:25.910
When we see this stuff, don't be

00:14:25.920 --> 00:14:29.310
alarmed; just know that it's a sign of

00:14:29.320 --> 00:14:31.990
the times.

00:14:31.990 --> 00:14:32.000
I

00:14:32.000 --> 00:14:34.749
also can't leave out

00:14:34.749 --> 00:14:34.759
another

00:14:34.759 --> 00:14:37.189
of my favorite books,

00:14:37.199 --> 00:14:38.749
'Seeing

00:14:38.749 --> 00:14:38.759
Jesus.'It's

00:14:38.759 --> 00:14:40.509
one of our

00:14:40.509 --> 00:14:40.519
favorites.

00:14:40.519 --> 00:14:43.829
It

00:14:43.839 --> 00:14:46.110
is a fiction book, so if you're not into

00:14:46.120 --> 00:14:47.990
fiction, this probably wouldn't be for

00:14:48.000 --> 00:14:50.430
you, but I will put it in my Goodreads

00:14:50.440 --> 00:14:52.870
link.

00:14:52.880 --> 00:14:55.150
Even though it's

00:14:55.160 --> 00:14:58.189
fiction, this person has definitely seen

00:14:58.199 --> 00:15:01.389
Jesus; he's had an encounter, because

00:15:01.399 --> 00:15:04.749
it is one of the most

00:15:04.759 --> 00:15:08.030
authentic experiences put into

00:15:08.040 --> 00:15:12.310
words. It describes a relationship

00:15:12.320 --> 00:15:15.230
where He walks with

00:15:15.240 --> 00:15:17.870
you and talks with you.

00:15:21.199 --> 00:15:23.310
The way he describes

00:15:23.320 --> 00:15:25.310
the visitations

00:15:25.320 --> 00:15:29.389
I've

00:15:29.389 --> 00:15:29.399
had—the

00:15:29.399 --> 00:15:31.389
way He sounds

00:15:31.389 --> 00:15:31.399
and

00:15:31.399 --> 00:15:34.590
talks—I'm

00:15:34.600 --> 00:15:39.030
telling you, the author, Jeffrey McClain Jones, claims it's fiction,

00:15:39.040 --> 00:15:41.670
but I'll leave it up to you to decide.

00:15:43.920 --> 00:15:46.509
He has a whole

00:15:46.519 --> 00:15:49.269
series,

00:15:49.269 --> 00:15:49.279
but

