00:18:17.039 --> 00:18:20.230
Father, open up their wombs. Your

00:18:20.230 --> 00:18:20.240
word

00:18:20.240 --> 00:18:22.029
in

00:18:22.039 --> 00:18:24.870
Malachi talks about

00:18:24.880 --> 00:18:28.310
how your seed will be blessed.

00:18:28.320 --> 00:18:30.669
I thank You

00:18:30.679 --> 00:18:32.630
that You heal whatever needs to be

00:18:32.640 --> 00:18:35.390
healed in their bodies right now.

00:18:37.080 --> 00:18:39.789
We thank You for

00:18:39.799 --> 00:18:43.590
creative miracles, that organs

00:18:43.600 --> 00:18:45.270
that need to be there are there.

00:18:47.400 --> 00:18:49.909
Bless

00:18:49.909 --> 00:18:49.919
the

00:18:49.919 --> 00:18:52.230
fruit of their womb, Father.

00:18:52.240 --> 00:18:54.669
I thank You

00:18:57.120 --> 00:19:00.669
for

00:19:26.240 --> 00:19:30.710
healthy, full-term

00:19:30.720 --> 00:19:34.270
