00:19:39.320 --> 00:19:42.990
They

00:19:42.990 --> 00:19:43.000
shall

00:19:43.000 --> 00:19:46.070
not have

00:19:51.720 --> 00:19:56.710
back pains, migraines,

00:19:56.710 --> 00:19:56.720
or

00:19:56.720 --> 00:19:59.789
issues

00:19:59.799 --> 00:20:02.230
the world says are a

00:20:02.230 --> 00:20:02.240
part of

00:20:02.240 --> 00:20:04.710
pregnancy.

