I rebuke

00:20:30.440 --> 00:20:33.950
colic in

00:20:33.960 --> 00:20:36.190
Jesus'name.

00:20:36.200 --> 00:20:38.830
We pray over the nursing—that it's easy, that the babies latch on, and that the milk is bountiful and painless. If they're doing formula, we pray

00:20:38.840 --> 00:20:40.909
