00:22:04.240 --> 00:22:06.029
Give them rest and

00:22:09.279 --> 00:22:10.830
strength.

00:22:13.240 --> 00:22:15.909
I thank You that

00:22:15.909 --> 00:22:15.919
there

00:22:18.190 --> 00:22:18.200
is

00:22:18.200 --> 00:22:20.190
no

00:22:20.200 --> 00:22:22.350
postpartum

00:22:24.120 --> 00:22:26.310
