00:22:32.840 --> 00:22:35.029
We

00:22:35.039 --> 00:22:37.590
thank

00:22:37.600 --> 00:22:40.750
You

00:22:40.760 --> 00:22:42.710
for

00:22:42.720 --> 00:22:44.630
great

00:22:44.640 --> 00:22:48.269
